Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:03.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一集的Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:06.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,随着我与四季两个新生加入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!成为了8人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:11.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,二年级的学姐果然都好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:12.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们试了各种方法想拉近跟学姐的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但总是不太理想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看见这样的我们的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:22.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一年级的鬼冢夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:25.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏美表示想要担任Liella!的制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 她似乎还有着不可告人的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,团名…吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:34.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,难得我们4个能作为Liella!的姐妹团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,当然需要一个新的团名了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:40.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:42.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(全力#)\N这个!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全力#?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:46.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(KIRARA!!)\N这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像杂志的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再说我们也不是Liella!的姐妹团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这 这我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:56.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想想…要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:57.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是小组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错 要取个小组名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,仅限这个夏天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:04.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:04.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们之所以要与学姐分开练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:10.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是因为想追上学姐们的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:13.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为我们想成为Liella!的力量去争夺优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:16.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是无法成为Liella!的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就不打算当学园偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,至少我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这 这我也明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就只是一个提议 提议而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比想象中还顽固呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还以为只要把人分开就能让我随心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不过夏美是不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那么 我们重振精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天就来拍摄各位的日常…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:48.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,来 奋战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掀起我们的旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爬上巅峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要拿下胜利!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:10.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不够 还不够 远远不够!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不论何时我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越昨天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟能走到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然仍旧不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:21.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还是要燃烧自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想与你一同欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想了解尚未知晓的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我还会更加成长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想轻易放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,现在立刻 Start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向顶点前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还要更加 更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更加情绪高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去实现吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在这瞬间 尽自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追寻梦想 尽自己全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:03:00.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为邂逅 给了我热情的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:07.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是不可能的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也去实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:11.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们会继续相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错 WE WILL!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,安安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我旁边那位把气氛弄得很沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这时候就轮到儿时玩伴出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在想我们到底哪里做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,做错了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,难得一年级的都加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:49.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还以为暑假可以大家一起开开心心练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她们不是也说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她们都说了想自己练习看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我认为那是件很棒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,默默等待她们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也是我们这些学姐该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们也要继续提升实力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,成为Galaxy的目标啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且暑假结束后就要地区预赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在那之前还有学园祭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#06 Dekkaidow!)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到希奈子的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:33.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不过这里还真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,环境清幽 空气新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,食物也很美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那么就先跑到希奈子家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么 你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们决定要在希奈子家集训啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,弯不回去…都是那辆巴士害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但为什么连我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为你说要摄影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你还说只要是为了制作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,无论什么地方都会跟我们去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贴身跟拍记录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:05.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,该说那只是场面话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还是我没想到会这么夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,帮你垫的交通费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Money…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,仅次于我性命 重要的money…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下来要一路跑到小希奈子家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跑步机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:38.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等 等等…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子的家在哪边?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,回转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好乖好乖 都长这么大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么可能好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们到底还要练到怎样才满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们决定要成为Liella!的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,它叫你打起精神来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你居然懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好了 换完衣服就来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们特地来这一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不要客气尽管吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好大的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们家是开民宿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:51.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常适合作为集训地点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:54.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,话说回来 小夏美好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她刚刚好像在房间里的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:04.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天要向大家介绍鬼夏风夏日精力冰沙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,冰沙的视频完全赚不到钱\N(活力满分 鬼夏风夏日冰沙)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就只好把今天的练习视频加工一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(超人气学园偶像 Liella! 内哄!?)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再弄得刺激点或许比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(超人气学园偶像 Liella! 即将解散!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不过视频内容就只是在练习而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反正这样就能让观看次数暴增
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Money也会跟着滚滚来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"Liella! 即将"…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已经要吃饭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,刚刚太专心剪片了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是我们今天练习的视频吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没什么好看的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是学姐们的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在想能不能用来宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这个舞台真的很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也跟小芽衣她们聊过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们的梦想就是要超越这个舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,梦想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们加入之后就多了一年级的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我们要能够超越这个舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:17.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,让Liella!的力量升级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就是你们的梦想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美的梦想又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是CEO对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你的目标是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我没什么…特别的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,硬要说的话 就是赚很多钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,当然是为了让自己老了之后不用烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 我要去吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你先过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 无聊透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(突袭! Liella!练习的样子!)\N(IN北海道!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这个 认真是认真的吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原来这么有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且留言也是一片好评
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我才说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不必觉得难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,应该积极上传视频才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全没在听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样学妹们或许就能有点自信了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不过 可不一定全是好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果因此自信过头的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们几个 不要给我站在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,从今天开始你们就是伴舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,性格这么扭曲的人只有堇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吐槽太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我更在意那个叫夏美的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她会特地来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我认为肯定是另有企图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也是一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:02.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,应该要找夏美学妹好好问清楚才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是她们人在北海道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千认为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我没在听
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我只是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然她们已经能做到这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为了帮她们增加自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把练习难度调高也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:30.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的梦想是将来在奥运拿下金牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:33.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美又是最后一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的梦想是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,成为拿到诺贝尔奖的科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的梦想是成为模特儿环游世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全长不高…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好讨厌的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟学姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跳一样的舞步?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我等等把详细动作传过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,记得看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,由于这的确会给你们带来压力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我本来想之后再找你们商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但看过那部视频后我认为应该没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:17.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,当然 这对现在的你们应该还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要暑假期间好好努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肯定能在学园祭前练好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要大家都达到同个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能增进所有人的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也能使我们更积极面对Love Live
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有个目标也比较容易规划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们的目标是Love Live优胜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,忘记了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:00.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然视频得到好评让人很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不过练习的难度也提升了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都学姐这么做太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明我们才刚开始练习而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是你的心灵鬼之补品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼冢夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天也要继续为大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,带来Liella!的练习视频哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们还没开始练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样看起来会像是在偷懒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,实际上就是在偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有很多原因的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,从外面就听得见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们的梦想是要超越那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:46.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们的梦想应该是超越学姐们的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就该负起责任才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:50.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样就想放弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:54.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也不想再听你们谈什么梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在拍摄视频时是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们的梦想决不是无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错 那是件非常美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:14.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拥有一个只要努力或许就能触及的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那么 我们就继续拍摄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,洗澡水的温度还可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不会 该道谢的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,白天真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也没说什么了不起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小夏美真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有个目标很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不是说我没有目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你太谦虚了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是没有目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又怎么会当CEO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就说了我真的没有什么目标啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是因为真的没有目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我才会像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,除了赚money就没什么事能做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下来我自己弄就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这次又是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季同学? 还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,熊…是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,该…该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要直接冲回民宿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不可能跑得过它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:39.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还是要装死?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:42.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行 听说那根本就没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是我 是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其实我是来把我爸爸忘记的东西带给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打扮成熊送来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是那时爸爸给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,难得都来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想说也给大家一点慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要对东京的大家保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:11.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 你就这么在意团员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也一样在意小夏美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我稍微听到了你跟小希奈子的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反正也没说什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就请香音学姐也来视频里露个脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你要不要来当学园偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:40.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我希望小夏美来当Liella!的第9位成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂你为什么要说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然你没有梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要试着跟大家一起追逐同个梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,梦想?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果小夏美你没有梦想的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我曾经拥有过许多梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也已经明白梦想是不会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟香音学姐这种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看得到梦想的人是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也受过了许多挫折哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我本来有个梦想是进入结丘的音乐班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最后却以失败告终了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 小可可跟大家教了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要跟大家一起 就有办法努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要互相弥补缺点跟不足之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能够一起追逐梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:40.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那么下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么样 感觉很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们要整齐划一地跳出这些舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在为我们加油的大家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这么一来 坐在观众席的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也会在心中一同起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整座舞台将合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那正是最棒的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为大家带来这样的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼夏好~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是你的心灵鬼之补品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鬼冢夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没想到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是结女的学园祭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:23.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不不不 就说别拍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,交给你了 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的 请大家尽情享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今年的演唱会我们更加有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:34.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比起这个 跟鬼夏的契约最后怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已经是Liella!的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么还在说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,集训时明明都练习那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不如说你是最卖力的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那么要开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这就是9个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全新的Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,6!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,7!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,8!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,9!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们今天要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,尽情享受!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:37.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用特技表演纵身一跃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跳过湛蓝的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,击掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,无论什么都能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Vivid季节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,淘气模式发动中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以就别客气了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏天是稍纵即逝 Happy的 最棒的Showtime
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一同起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:58.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Clap your hands☆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗨起来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,尽情玩乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:07.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没玩个尽兴就太逊·太逊·太逊了~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Say Yeah Yeah Yeah Yeah~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Funky coconut
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们是juicy的盛夏宠儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,状况十分良好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Heaven Heaven Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Oh Babababy~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Crazy coconut
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,浸染纯白的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Vitamin SUMMER!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,让我嗨到最高点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Heaven Heaven Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah Yeah Yeah~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Bababy~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah Yeah Yeah~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Bababy~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,…透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是…棒透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:02.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:12.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的梦想前方 总是能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名为希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:20.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在闪烁着 闪烁耀眼光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的梦想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟会走向何处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,场场相遇之中 虽然又会迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请试着去享受这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,觉得「似乎能做到却做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最后做到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就会很开心 想着要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整颗心都像是要跳了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,尽情欢笑 放声高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,继续走向远方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界广阔无边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然也有景色会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但热情会始终如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越许多后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想实现的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,来吧 大家一起去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要弹奏出什么样的悸动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改变未来吧!
